comments: Bell (GSW) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Wade (MIA) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Winslow (MIA) and Curry (GSW) make incidental contact with one another while the ball is loose.
Adebayo (MIA) maintains legal guarding position on Curry (GSW), who dribbles the ball off of his leg and loses control of it.
Durant (GSW) does not extend his leg unnaturally and Adebayo (MIA) steps on his foot, affecting his ability to land safely following the jump shot attempt.
LLB shows Iguodala (GSW) makes contact with Olynyk's (MIA) arm that affects his ability to pass.
LLS shows Iguodala (GSW) reaches in and makes clean contact with the ball during Adebayo's (MIA) upward shooting motion.
Bell (GSW) firms up in a screening position in Adebayo's (MIA) path and does not deliver the contact.
Olynyk (MIA) makes clean contact with the ball on the pass by Durant (GSW).
Adebayo (MIA) firms up in a screening position in Iguodala's (GSW) path and does not deliver the contact.
Bell (GSW) makes incidental contact with Richardson (MIA) after he grabs the rebound.
Winslow (MIA) commits a take foul on Bell (GSW).
Olynyk (MIA) firms up in a screening position in Bell's (GSW) path and absorbs the contact.
Bell (GSW) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Wade (MIA) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Dragic (MIA) commits a take foul on Durant (GSW).
Wade (MIA) fumbles the ball during his dribble and upon retrieval, maintains his established pivot foot and legally makes the pass.
Bell (GSW) legally contests Wade's (MIA) jump shot attempt.

Wade's (MIA) initial shot attempt is blocked by Bell (GSW) and Wade legally regains possession of the ball when he returns to the floor and attempts another shot prior to the expiration of the game clock.
